{"tid":2032153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁愛詩：彭定康批評港版國安法前未搞清楚","createTime":"2020-05-24T01:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T07:49:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"83813e7cb400a8f73b4d8e6f42dd9edc2643985f","tid":2032153,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:57:31.000Z","msg":"前港督彭定康及英國前外相聶偉敬發起聯署，譴責北京實施港版國安法，有近200名來自美、英等政界人士參與。<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會前副主任、前律政司長梁愛詩在本台節目上表示，港版國安法的法律條文未出爐，認為彭定康等人未搞清楚，已經作出批評，強調港版國安法不會攻擊香港的自治權，更加不會打擊法治，立法原則亦列明不能侵害香港市民的基本自由，並不牴觸一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n至於港版國安法的審判權屬於中央抑或特區，梁愛詩認為，原則上審判權屬於犯罪地，因此政府去年才有移交逃犯的考慮。被問到日後有市民高叫港獨口號，會否觸犯分裂國家及顛覆政權罪，梁愛詩認為要視乎有否鼓吹及煽動元素，無法隨便揣測。"},{"pid":"762b1004cc5add091e2ee48b38b664958d589b2b","tid":2032153,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289728&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=606e283f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289728</a>"},{"pid":"5ba8edee0ff8e190a63e5c40dd9f59cca702fad1","tid":2032153,"uid":25260,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"而家係邊個未搞清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd1a35f29fee112255214d2ea7c0acd97322f33","tid":2032153,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:02:23.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"702add113eb6496b542b54ac0ce38179f67b1c54","tid":2032153,"uid":254450,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"當初送中條例都好似係咁解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40956e027780a9fcdfa611b8377299cb9b4cc6a","tid":2032153,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply